.TH "RTCTRANSPORTSTATS.LOCALCERTIFICATEID" "3JS" "June 24, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
RTCTransportStats.localCertificateId \- RTCTransportStats:
localCertificateId property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]localCertificateId\f[B]\f[R] property of the
\f[CR]RTCTransportStats\f[R] dictionary is a string that indicates the
id of the local certificate used by this \f[CR]RTCIceTransport\f[R].
.PP
It is only present for DTLS transports, and after DTLS has been
negotiated.
.SH VALUE
A string that containing the id of the local certificate used by this
transport.
